  <md:title>Watergate: Nixon’s Domestic Nightmare</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list id="list-00001">
<item>Describe the actions that Nixon and his confederates took to ensure his reelection in 1972</item>
<item>Explain the significance of the Watergate crisis</item>
<item>Describe Gerald Ford’s domestic policies and achievements in foreign affairs</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>64297b67-61f1-490a-b3b0-adfbf040cc53</md:uuid>
